Music Player (Privacy Policy)
Privacy policy
This privacy policy (“Policy”) describes how Eco Mobile (“Eco Mobile”, “we”, “us” or “our”) collects, protects, and uses the personally identifiable information (“Personal Information”) you (“User”, “you” or “your”) may provide in the Yaya Show mobile application and any of its products (collectively, “Eco Mobile”). It also describes the choices available to you regarding our use of your Personal Information and how you can access and update this information. This Policy does not apply to the practices of companies that we do not own or control, or to individuals that we do not employ or manage.
